touch config.example.env
```

Open it and add:
```
# Google Calendar
# Your Gmail address or Google Calendar ID
CALENDAR_ID=your-gmail@gmail.com

# Google Service Account
# Download from Google Cloud Console → IAM & Admin → Service Accounts → Keys → Add Key → JSON
# Paste the entire JSON contents as a single line
SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON={"type":"service_account","project_id":"...","private_key_id":"...","private_key":"...","client_email":"...","client_id":"..."}

# VAPI
# Get from https://dashboard.vapi.ai/keys
VAPI_PUBLIC_KEY=your-vapi-public-key